---
layout: post
title: Event Guidelines
description: To do for running an event at Pi.
---
## As soon as the event is planned
Plan stage setup at noon, and removal at night.

## Setup
Place 30 seats in the main room, with additional seats in the metting room.
Charge mic and presenter.
Get a HDMI Mac  adapter, just in case.
Get slide.
Check slide on TV.
Put some water on the stage
desk for hostess
desk for TNP
reverve seats if required

## During the event
Have a person to help removing seats
have a person to sync service with catering
check air conditioning
